<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Denier" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Denier,</orth> the smallest piece of money: <emph>not a d.</emph>  <bibl n="shak. shr 1.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. Ind. I, 9</bibl>. <cit><quote>I'll not pay a d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.91" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 91</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my dukedom to a beggarly d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.252" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 252</bibl></cit>.
